{
  "subject": "You're live \u2014 your mentor profile is now on OpenMentor",
  "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n<title>You're live</title>\n</head>\n<body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#EDEBE4;\">\n<div style=\"display:none;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;\">Your profile is live \u2014 here's how to get your first request</div>\n<table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#EDEBE4\">\n<tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:32px 12px;\">\n<table role=\"presentation\" width=\"600\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:600px;max-width:600px;background:#FFFFFF;border-radius:14px;border:1px solid #DEDBD1;\">\n<tr><td bgcolor=\"#CDE8C6\" style=\"padding:28px 40px;border-radius:14px 14px 0 0;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://openmentor.io/brand/logo/png/icon-app/icon-app-128.png\" width=\"44\" height=\"44\" alt=\"OpenMentor\" style=\"display:block;margin:0 auto;border:0;\"><div style=\"padding-top:16px;font:bold 26px/1.2 Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#161A20;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:-0.5px;\">You're live \ud83c\udf89</div></td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:24px 40px 0;\"><div style=\"font:normal 15px/1.6 Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#161A20;\">Hi {{first_name}},</div><div style=\"padding-top:10px;font:normal 15px/1.6 Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#5B6270;\">Your mentor profile passed review and is now visible in the OpenMentor catalog. New mentorship requests land in your dashboard \u2014 sign in any time with a magic link, no password needed.</div><table role=\"presentation\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"margin-top:18px;\"><tr><td width=\"4\" bgcolor=\"#17C3B2\" style=\"border-radius:2px;\"></td><td style=\"padding:14px 16px;background:#F7F6F2;border-radius:0 10px 10px 0;\"><div style=\"font:normal 13px/1.6 Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#4A5160;\">Profiles with a photo and 3+ tags get their first request faster.</div></td></tr></table></td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:24px 40px 0;\" align=\"center\"><table role=\"presentation\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\"><tr><td bgcolor=\"#132A52\" style=\"border-radius:12px;\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"{{mentor_profile_url}}\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:15px 30px;font:bold 15px Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#FFFFFF;text-decoration:none;\">See your public profile</a></td><td width=\"10\"></td><td style=\"border:2px solid #2F5EFF;border-radius:12px;\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://openmentor.io/mentor/login\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:13px 24px;font:bold 15px Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#132A52;text-decoration:none;\">Open dashboard</a></td></tr></table></td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:26px 40px 28px;\" align=\"center\"><div style=\"border-top:1px solid #DEDBD1;padding-top:16px;font:normal 11px/1.6 Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#5B6270;\">openmentor.io \u00b7 free mentorship for the tech community</div></td></tr>\n</table>\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n</body>\n</html>",
  "text": "Hi {{first_name}},\n\nYour mentor profile passed review and is now visible in the OpenMentor catalog:\n{{mentor_profile_url}}\n\nNew mentorship requests land in your dashboard \u2014 sign in any time with a magic link, no password needed:\nhttps://openmentor.io/mentor/login\n\nTip: profiles with a photo and 3+ tags get their first request faster.\n\n---\nopenmentor.io \u00b7 free mentorship for the tech community\nhttps://openmentor.io"
}
